# Random Even Number Table Generator

A simple Java console application that generates a **P × P** table with random even numbers (2–16), highlights a user-selected even number, and counts its occurrences.

## Features
- Generates random even numbers (2–16)
- Validates user input
- Highlights the selected number
- Displays the occurrence count

## Technologies
- Java
- Scanner
- Random
- Exception Handling

## Run

```bash
javac Table.java
java Table
```

